# Fleet sites

Registry: `config/fleet.json` — update when adding routes or sites.

## Patterns

- Shared UI: `@synthaembed/ui-fleet` (FleetShell, LiveSearchPanel, tokens)
- API: site BFF routes call `core-api` with workspace key from env — not Postgres
- Multi-site edit: `pnpm exec node --experimental-strip-types packages/cli/src/index.ts fleet context [siteId]`

## Active Phase A sites

hub · research-rag (arxiviq) · dumbmodel · benchmark-lab · finance-lab (stub)

Claim SITE-* tasks from work queue. Run `pnpm --filter @synthaembed/<site> dev` or `pnpm dev:fleet`.

